GenderNexus is bringing transgender and nonbinary communities together across Indiana to foster a community that is healthy, informed, and empowered by increasing access to care in all seven dimensions of wellness.



 By providing a safe space for community engagement, GenderNexus can help navigate and eradicate social and systemic barriers.



