HFF's ultimate goal is to end family homelessness. Until then, we will be a transformational force for families in housing, economic and educational stability. We can achieve this goal by providing wraparound programming that supports entire families overcoming or at-risk for homelessness, educating children and addressing the multiple systemic barriers the families we serve encounter on their road to stability.

